{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-understanding-questions-and-answers/task-13","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"zh-a1-learn-understanding-questions-and-answers","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Liu Ming daje negativan odgovor na pitanje Wang Hua <ruby>你是中国人吗<rp>(</rp><rt>nǐ shì zhōng guó rén ma</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>？ Hajde da istražimo kako koristi specifičnu negacionu reč.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p><ruby>不是<rp>(</rp><rt>bù shì</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> to pokazuje negiranje. Govoreći <ruby>我不是中国人<rp>(</rp><rt>wǒ bù shì zhōng guó rén</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>。, Liu Ming negira da je kineski. Zatim nastavlja sa <ruby>我是新加坡人<rp>(</rp><rt>wǒ shì xīn jiā pō rén</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>。, govoreći da je Msingapoa.</p>\n</section>","helpCategory":"Chinese Curriculum","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušaj zvuk odgovora na pitanje koje se nalazi ispod.</p>\n</section>","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-chinese/zh-a1-learn-understanding-questions-and-answers/task-13"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Kako odgovara Liu Ming?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Kaže da je kinesac.</p>","feedback":"<p>Zapravo kaže da nije kinesac.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Kaže da nije Mchina, već Msingapoa.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Kaže da ne zna odakle je.</p>","feedback":"<p>Opisuje svoju naciju jasno.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Kaže da je Kanadastan.</p>","feedback":"<p>Nisi spomenuo/spomenula Kanadu uopšte.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":2}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company1-breakroom.png","characters":[{"character":"Liu Ming","position":{"x":50,"y":17,"z":1.4},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ZH_A1_greetings_and_introductions_dialogue.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":10.55,"finishTimestamp":14